measurements.description: Five-hundred fifty flowers and 28 buds on 50 pendant inflorescences; fully displayed around a 161x119-cm cleanly grown plant in a 20-cm plastic azalea pot, bark media; sepals and petals pale chartreuse, midrib maroon; lip pale yellow, side lobes striped maroon, midlobe velvet dark maroon, calli ochre; column black-maroon, anther cap yellow; substance medium; texture glossy.
